# Salsify API Reference

This MCP server integrates with **Salsify PIM API v1** at `https://app.salsify.com/api/v1/orgs/{orgId}`.

Official docs:
- Overview: https://developers.salsify.com/docs
- Products: https://developers.salsify.com/docs/product-object
- Filter syntax: https://developers.salsify.com/reference/salsify-filtering-language-syntax

## Conventions

- Auth: `Authorization: Bearer {api_token}`
- Credentials via `X-Salsify-Api-Token` and `X-Salsify-Org-Id` headers or env vars
- Bulk ID lookups use HTTP `REPORT` method with body `{ "ids": [...] }`
- Enumerated/picklist values: `GET https://app.salsify.com/api/orgs/{orgId}/enumerated_values?property_id={propertyId}` (non-v1 org app API)
- v1 executes read operations only; write routes are documented via recommend tool
